dc_description_s: Inter American Geodetic Survey. Relief shown by 10 meters contour interval and spot heights. "Las lineas negras numeradas indican cada kilómetro de la cuadrícula Lambert, Costa Rica norte. Las tres últimas cifras de los números de la cuadrícula han sido omitidas." Includes diagram showing administrative boundaries. Includes index to schools, churches, public buildings, and points of interest Standard map series designation: Serie E 964 = [Series] E 964.
dc_publisher_s: San José, Costa Rica : Instituto Geográfico Nacional, 1982.
